/**
 * Root Level Server Configuration Files
 * 
 * .env: Environment variables for local development
 * 
 * .gitignore: Specifies files that Git should ignore
 * 
 * docker-compose.yml: Docker Compose configuration for local development
 *   - Defines services like the database, server, etc.
 *   - Sets up networking between containers
 *   - Configures volumes for persistent data
 * 
 * Dockerfile.server: Docker configuration for building the server container
 *   - Specifies the base image
 *   - Copies source code
 *   - Installs dependencies
 *   - Sets up the build process
 *   - Configures the container runtime
 * 
 * eslint.config.mjs: ESLint configuration for code linting
 *   - Defines coding style rules
 *   - Configures plugins and extensions
 * 
 * jest.config.mjs: Jest configuration for testing
 *   - Sets up test environment
 *   - Configures test coverage reporting
 *   - Specifies test file patterns
 * 
 * index.ts: Main application entry point
 *   - Initializes the Express application
 *   - Sets up global middleware
 *   - Connects to the database
 *   - Registers routes
 *   - Starts the server
 */